class=3DMsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p>Good day Kgotodia and =
all,<o:p></o:p></p><p>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p>Thank you for your email. =
<o:p></o:p></p><p>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p>Every section within a =
sectional title scheme has a participation quota (PQ), which is =
calculated by expressing the size of each section (floor area) as a =
percentage of the total sizes of all sections (% of a =
whole).<o:p></o:p></p><p>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p>Transvalia's 20 =
sections are all the same size (32 square meters) and so everyone's PQ =
values are the same (32 SQM / 640 SQM =3D 0.0500 =
PQ).<o:p></o:p></p><p>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p>The PQ schedule of a =
sectional title scheme has three effects:<o:p></o:p></p><ol start=3D1 =
type=3D1><li class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l2 =
level1 lfo2'>It determines the size of the undivided share of the common =
property the owner of that section owns.<o:p></o:p></li><li =
class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l2 =
level1 lfo2'>It determines the value of that owner&#8217;s =
vote.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3DMsoNormal =
style=3D'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l2 =
level1 lfo2'>It determines the share of the annual levy and other =
expenses that owner must pay.<o:p></o:p></li></ol><p>Although, removing =
water and electricity expenses from your levy and adding these charges =
as separate items, will decrease the normal levy amount - you will find =
that the total charges on your statements will increase by approximately =
30%.<o:p></o:p></p><p>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p>This is the only way we =
will be able to cover all the scheme's expenses (council bill, =
insurance, maintenance, audit, =
etc.).<o:p></o:p></p><p>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p>I hope the above =
clarifies, but if you have any further queries, please don't hesitate to =
contact us. We look forward to your responses to the highlighted =
matters.<o:p></o:p></p><p>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p>Sincerely,<o:p></o:p></=
